tiwari, bahuguna ke kushasan, kumbh va starjia prakaran par mook rahe  nai dilli(pyau). loksabhaa chunaav 2014 main desh kii janata ne jahaan manamohani kushasan se mukti ke liye narendra modi kaa aitihaasik samarthan de kar purna bahumat se sattashin karne kaa kaary kiya. desh kii janata dwaara sushasan kii aash main diye is samarthan kii aad main kuch padlolupu uttrakhand bhaajapai netaa devbhumi uttrakhand main rajya gathan ke 13 saal baad sattashin pehali janhiton ke liye samarpit harish ravat kii sarkaar ko giraane ke liye narendra modi ko gumraah kar rahe hai.  aaj uttrakhand kii janata ne kendra main asin rahi manamohani kushasan ko ukhaad phenkane va desh main sushasan ko sthapit karne ke liye narendra modi ko khulaa samarthan diya he. na kii pradesh main rajya gathan ke baad pehali baar janaankankshaon ko saakaar karne ke liye samarpit ho kar kaam kar rahi harish ravat kii sarkaar ko giraane ke liye.  desh ke jananaayak modi ko is baat kaa ahsaas hoga ki uttrakhand main ab tak jitani bhi bhaajapa va congress kii sarkarein rahi (tiwari, khandudi, nishank va bahuguna aadi )unhone pradesh kii janaankankshaon ko saakaar karne ke bajaay unka galaa ghontne kaa kaam kiya.   aise janhiton ko nirmamata se raundne vaale kushasako va gat varsh kaa kedarghati main aayi traasadee se ubarne main kargar sabit ho rahe pradesh ke vartmaan mukhyamantri harish ravat kii sarkaar ko kaaphi aashaayein he. jis prakaar se mukhyamantri harish ravat ne apane chand mahine ke shashan main kai jamini kaary karke janata ke dammagaate vishwaas ko patari main laane kaa kaam kiya. uske baad pradesh kii janata ko laga ki pehali baar apni koi sarkaar sattashin hui he. khaskakar jo sarkaar garesenn ke sapane ko saakaar karne ke liye krit sankalpit ho, jo sarkaar kii janata ke sarkaron se utar chuke vishwaas ko patari par laa sakati he, jo sarkaar bhrashtachari naukarshahon va netaaon ke gathjod par ankush laga saktaa he. jo uttrakhand janaankankshaon ko saakaar karne ke liye krit sankalpit he.  nahin to purvavarti tiwari, khandudi, nishank va bahuguna kii sarkaron ne jis nirmamata se pradesh kii janaankakshaon ko raundne kaa kaam kiya tha usase janata kaa vishwaas hi tut gaya tha. jis prakaar se purvavarti sarkaron ne mujfarnagarkand ke doshiyon ko sangrakshan dene, gairsann par chhalane, jansankhya par aadhaarit parisemen thopane, bhrashtachar ke krityon se janata ko chhalane kaa kaary hi kiya. pradesh kii janata main abhi kumbh ghotaale va starjia ghotaale va bahuguna ke kushasan ke dansh abhi bhi vyathit kar rahe he. aise main naitikta kii duhai dene vaale bhaajapa ke tamaam netaa chaahe khandudi ho yaa nishank yaa satpal maharaj inamen se kisi ko bhi naitikta kii duhai dene kaa haq nahin he. ye netaa bataaye ki ye log starjia, kumbh prakaran , tiwari va bahuguna ke kushasan aadi par kyon sharmnaak mook rakhe hue the. kyon inhone mujfarnagar kand-94 ke gunaahagaaron va mulaayam ke kaharon ko sangrakshan dene kaa kaam kiya. kyon ne netaa apane sankeern swaarth ke peeche pradesh ko baandhon main duubon kar barbaad karne ke liye jute hue the ? kyon inhone jansankhya par aadhaarit parisemen par mook saadh kar pradesh ke hiton ko raundne kaa kaary kiya.===============	CAG

kaaphi he or usame se bhi kuch to rishwat ke naam par bali chad jaataa he. or naa hi kuch bhavishya ke liye jamaa ho rahaa he. #sanvida_karmi_maang_karte_rahete_he_or_kaam_chalata_rahata he. sthai hone ke sapane se hi unka pet bhar jaataa he. aazaadee ke itane saalo baad bhi #hamaare_desh main #karmchaariyon ke ek varg kii ye haalat hogi ye soch soch ke hi main aksar kaap jaataa hoon. #uttar_pradesh_sarkaar ko agar itani si baat samaj aa jaae kii #har_varg_ke_liye_mahagaai_ek_saamaan_bad rahi he to vetan bhi ek samaan nahin to kam se kam do vakt kii roti achche se mil sake itnaa to hona hi chahie. abhi puure #desh main #aarakshan par bahut charchaa chal rahi he. mat ghabaraao mere savinda karmiyon wo din dur nahin he jab #sanvida_ek_jaati ban jaaygi or sanvida karmi or unke parivaar ko aarakshan dena hoga. bhagwaan kii krupa sanvida karmi par bani rahe or un par mahangaai kaa asar naa ho varanaa jis tarah se #kisaano_ko_aatmahatya kerani pad rahi he usee prakaar mere bhaaiyo ko bhi aatm hatya kerani pade.#uttar_pradesh ke #mukhyamantri mananeey #yogi_adityanath ji ko ab is ore bhi vishesh dhyaan dene kii aavashyaktaa he.  ishwar se ek prarthana or karata hoon kii hamaari sarkaar ko or mere sthai karmchaaree bhaaiyo ko ahsaas ho kii sanvida karmi bhi ek insaan he jaanavar nahin.    \U0001f33ais post ko adhik se adhik share karen shaayad kisi ke aankhon kaanon tak hamaari baat pahunch jaae.\U0001f33a isi aashaa ke saath.....  aapkaa shubh chintak akaash treepathi #pradesh_adhyaksh  gram rojgaar sevak sanghathan,u0 pra0	OAG

naastik he or jaya, bhagwaan se naaraaz hokar gaanaa gaati he, lekin sherkhan ek sachcha insaan he.  4/ film 'shaan" main amitabh bachchan or shashi kapur sadhu ke vesh main janata ko thagte hai, lekin isi film main "abdul" aisa sachcha insaan he jo sachai ke liye jaan de detaa he.  5/ film "kranti" main mata kaa bhajan karne vaala raja (pradeep kumaar) gaddaar he or karimkhan (shatrughna sinha) ek mahaan deshbhakt, jo desh ke liye apni jaan de detaa he.  6/ amar-akbar-anthoni main teenon bacchon kaa baap kishanlaal ek khooni smagaller he lekin unke bacchon (akbar or anthoni) ko paalane vaale muslim or isai mahaan insaan he.  7/ kul milakar aapako, 'saleem-javed' kii filmon main, hindu naastik milegaa yaa phir dharm kaa uphaas karata hua koi karnama dikhegaa jabaki sherkhan pathan, DSP disuja, abdul, padri, maaikel, dabid, aadi jaise adarsh charitra dekhne ko milenge.  8/ ho saktaa he aapane pehle kabhi is par dhyaan na diya ho, lekin abaki baar zaraa dhyaan se dekhnaa keval 'saleem/javed' kii hi nahin, balki kadar khan, kaifi azmi, mahesh bhatta, aadi kii filmon kaa bhi yahi haal he.   9/ film industry par daaud jaison kaa niyantran rahaa he. isamen aksar aparaadhiyon kaa mahimamandan kiya jaataa he or 'pandit' ko dhoort, thakur ko jaalim, 'banie' ko soodakhor, 'sardaar' ko murkh kamedian aadi hi dikhaaya jaataa he.  10/ 'farhaan akhtar' kii film
